WEBVTT

00:00:15.908 --> 00:00:17.842
WYSIEDLENIE. di ershte ib-

00:00:19.705 --> 00:00:22.275
kent ir nemen nokh a mol redn

00:00:22.275 --> 00:00:24.870
vegn likvidatsye fun Byale geto?

00:00:24.784 --> 00:00:25.540
yo.

00:00:25.540 --> 00:00:28.915
UND d- ALSO t- vegn di ershte WYSIEDLENIE

00:00:28.915 --> 00:00:31.359
⟨dos⟩ iz gevezn dem zekstn

00:00:31.669 --> 00:00:35.274
dem zekstn, dem zek- dem zekstn

00:00:36.158 --> 00:00:37.907
tsvey un fertsik.

00:00:38.149 --> 00:00:43.571
ALSO. nakher UNK vi der yudnrat hot genumen unterhandlen, hot men oysgehandlt

00:00:43.571 --> 00:00:44.741
oyf geyn

00:00:45.287 --> 00:00:48.841
nor di vos arbetn nisht geyn tsum ershtn.

00:00:49.067 --> 00:00:52.470
UND di vos arbetn hobn gekrign aroys tsetlen

00:00:52.695 --> 00:00:57.279
yeder eyner hot gehat, ikh hob gekrign tsum bayshpil far mir, far mayn FRAU, far mayn kind

00:00:57.353 --> 00:00:59.675
hob ikh gekrign tsetlen az zey kenen blaybn.

00:01:01.622 --> 00:01:04.873
in letstn moment, ven ale zenen avek fun shtub

00:01:05.571 --> 00:01:09.092
mit der, mit der ershter WYSIEDLENIE iz avek mayn

00:01:09.351 --> 00:01:10.880
mayn VATER

00:01:11.106 --> 00:01:13.850
mit STIEFMUTTER mit di tokhter.

00:01:14.143 --> 00:01:15.757
mayn onkl

00:01:15.932 --> 00:01:17.107
⟨Zele⟩

00:01:17.485 --> 00:01:19.740
mit dray fir kinder

00:01:20.708 --> 00:01:23.925
di klenste, vayl di gresere zenen shoyn nisht gevezn mit im

00:01:24.201 --> 00:01:27.418
der f- der o- der onkl Pinkhes

00:01:27.694 --> 00:01:29.527
hot gehat bay zikh

00:01:29.820 --> 00:01:34.685
fr- kinder fun Varshe, zenen gevezn UNK a por

00:01:34.685 --> 00:01:36.297
tsvey kleyne kinder

00:01:36.297 --> 00:01:38.944
zenen gekumen tsu ⟨dem⟩ tante tsu mayne

00:01:39.118 --> 00:01:41.069
un zenen ale mitgegangen.

00:01:42.122 --> 00:01:44.090
mayn shver iz geganen

00:01:44.367 --> 00:01:45.913
mayn SCHWIEGERVATER

00:01:45.953 --> 00:01:48.107
iz gegangen mit zayn bruder

00:01:49.041 --> 00:01:51.094
un mitn SOHN

00:01:51.741 --> 00:01:54.249
un der SO- dem SOHN's kind

00:01:54.424 --> 00:01:55.155
UND

00:01:55.155 --> 00:01:56.260
di froy

00:01:56.260 --> 00:01:58.046
UND di froy's a shvester

00:01:58.423 --> 00:02:01.437
un dem SCHWIEGERVATER's a BRUDER.

00:02:02.288 --> 00:02:05.016
di zenen avekgegangen mit di ershte WYSIEDLENIE.

00:02:06.760 --> 00:02:10.432
ale zenen gevorn farzamlt oyfn shul hoyf

00:02:10.793 --> 00:02:11.917
in Byale

00:02:12.160 --> 00:02:16.744
UND fun dortn UNK farzamlte

00:02:16.767 --> 00:02:19.877
iz GEKOMMEN shoyn der UNK GESTAPO

00:02:19.877 --> 00:02:21.891
m'hot zey gefirt langzam

00:02:21.897 --> 00:02:23.353
tsu di

00:02:23.353 --> 00:02:24.556
statsye

00:02:24.732 --> 00:02:26.374
di ban statsye

00:02:26.374 --> 00:02:28.420
zenen zey aroyf oyf di rampe

00:02:29.322 --> 00:02:32.508
UND oyf di rampe, oyf di fi rampe, me flegt a mol

00:02:32.508 --> 00:02:36.482
ladeven f- gruzeven fi

00:02:36.482 --> 00:02:40.650
fun dortn zenen ge- zenen, hobn, hot men avekgeshtelt ale yidn.

00:02:40.650 --> 00:02:43.878
der tsug iz nokh nisht gevezn, zenen zey gevezn a ⟨gantse⟩ tog

00:02:43.935 --> 00:02:45.161
mitvokh

00:02:45.268 --> 00:02:47.661
zenen zey geshtanen a ⟨gantse⟩ tog nokh

00:02:47.661 --> 00:02:49.616
dort oyf di statsye

00:02:50.382 --> 00:02:51.962
oyf di ban statsye.

00:02:53.908 --> 00:02:56.411
ikh hob a por mol geganen tsu zey

00:02:56.411 --> 00:03:01.322
yedes mol hob ikh epes tsugetrogn. eyn mol hob ikh mitgenumen a krig vaser.

00:03:01.322 --> 00:03:04.284
a tsveyte mol hob ikh ge- hot men ongekokht

00:03:04.284 --> 00:03:06.190
shtshav borsht

00:03:06.190 --> 00:03:09.461
un ikh hob aroyfgegebn zey in WAGEN un arayngegebn zey.

00:03:11.172 --> 00:03:12.381
UND

00:03:13.737 --> 00:03:18.754
azoy iz dos gegangen. dos letste mol bin ikh geven, iz shoyn geven, der WAG- der transport iz shoyn gevezn.

00:03:18.754 --> 00:03:19.960
hob ikh ayngegebn

00:03:19.960 --> 00:03:23.290
shoyn mitog in der fri oder UNK ⟨gedenk⟩ nisht tsi

00:03:23.290 --> 00:03:26.440
s'hot angefangen mitv- donershtik, dinstik oder

00:03:26.440 --> 00:03:29.761
mitvokh. UNK ALSO hobn ibergenekhtikt oyf der rampe.

00:03:31.320 --> 00:03:32.512
UND nakher

00:03:33.362 --> 00:03:38.894
di ban iz geven badint fun ukrainer oder

00:03:38.894 --> 00:03:40.699
v- litviner

00:03:40.699 --> 00:03:43.751
hobn badint di, di ban

00:03:43.892 --> 00:03:45.711
di, di, di, dem tsug.

00:03:45.711 --> 00:03:47.902
m'hot nisht gevust vu der tsug geyt.

00:03:49.039 --> 00:03:54.107
nu, nakher hot men geshikt a gevisn IVANITSKI, a gevisn BAHNBEAMTER

00:03:54.107 --> 00:03:56.104
UND er iz geforn

00:03:56.548 --> 00:03:59.394
dervisn zikh vu der tsug iz avekgegangen.

00:03:59.890 --> 00:04:02.991
hot er gegangen fun statsye ts- biz statsye

00:04:02.991 --> 00:04:04.080
biz vanen es

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:05.430
hot zikh dervust

00:04:05.430 --> 00:04:06.197
az zenen

00:04:06.197 --> 00:04:09.164
gegangen, der tsug iz gegangen nokh SOBIBOR

00:04:09.205 --> 00:04:13.496
dortn in farnikhtungs lager. mir hobn tsum ershtn nisht gevust GARnisht vegn SOBIBOR

00:04:13.496 --> 00:04:17.006
nor yetst, khotsh eyn transport iz shoyn gegangen a mol

00:04:17.006 --> 00:04:18.293
keyn SOBIBOR

00:04:18.503 --> 00:04:22.086
mit ferd un WAGEN hot men gefirt gaystik kranke

00:04:22.086 --> 00:04:25.669
hot men oysgeSCHARTET fun di g- algemeyne bafelkerung

00:04:25.742 --> 00:04:30.410
un m'hot zey gefirt, loyt vi me ken zikh shoyn yetst forshteln

00:04:30.433 --> 00:04:32.303
az s'iz do a SOBIBOR

00:04:32.303 --> 00:04:37.416
un ze- m'hot zey gefirt keyn SOBIBOR, un dortn zenen zey farnikhtet gevorn, di gaystik kranke

00:04:37.416 --> 00:04:39.371
dos iz gevezn nokh in april

00:04:39.810 --> 00:04:48.490
un demolts hot ir gevust vos es heyst SOBIBOR, az men derharget yidn dort, tsi ir hot nor gevust az me firt zey UNK

00:04:48.523 --> 00:04:51.605
m'hot zikh, m'hot zikh shoyn a bisl forgeshtelt.

00:04:52.708 --> 00:04:55.891
gants rikhtik hot men gevoyr gevorn yetst

00:04:55.965 --> 00:04:59.249
az in di lagern vern yidn gemordet

00:05:00.066 --> 00:05:02.068
yetst shpeter shoyn

00:05:02.344 --> 00:05:03.924
in AUGUST

00:05:04.707 --> 00:05:09.555
fun Mezritsh, fun shtetl, s'iz lebn, lebn Byale, finef un tsvontsik kilometer

00:05:09.555 --> 00:05:11.116
iz fun Mezritsh

00:05:11.116 --> 00:05:14.522
s'iz eyner, eynem gelungen vos er iz shoyn gevezn

00:05:14.545 --> 00:05:16.614
in f-

00:05:16.789 --> 00:05:19.365
f- in, in TREBLINKA

00:05:20.130 --> 00:05:25.797
hot er arayn in di bakleydung vu m'hot s- gezamlt di kleyder, i- di kleyder fun di

00:05:25.797 --> 00:05:26.961
farnikhtete

00:05:26.961 --> 00:05:29.034
iz er geblibn in WAGEN

00:05:29.125 --> 00:05:33.357
un er iz tsurikgeforn UNK geshprungen fun WAGEN az zey kumen fun MIEDZYRZEC

00:05:33.357 --> 00:05:35.463
un hot dertseylt vos se kumt for

00:05:35.892 --> 00:05:36.780
in

00:05:37.191 --> 00:05:38.411
TREBLINKA

00:05:38.411 --> 00:05:42.737
hot men zikh shoyn forgeshtelt az z- az di zelbike makht men oykhet in SOBIBOR.

00:05:43.603 --> 00:05:45.436
m'hot oykh nisht gevust

00:05:45.544 --> 00:05:47.461
shpeter in Brisk

00:05:48.261 --> 00:05:51.776
in Brisk hot men bald oyf di drite vokh

00:05:51.776 --> 00:05:54.026
nokh

00:05:55.213 --> 00:05:56.779
oyf di drite vokh

00:05:56.779 --> 00:05:58.819
vi di DEUTSCHEN hobn bazetst

00:05:59.128 --> 00:06:00.269
Brisk

00:06:01.035 --> 00:06:04.370
hot men a- a- tsunoyfgeshtelt ale mener

00:06:04.461 --> 00:06:07.504
fun tsvelf biz zekhtsik

00:06:07.504 --> 00:06:11.964
un m'hot zey ergets aroysgefirt, un m'hot nisht gevust UNK dos iz. s'iz geven efsher zeks zibn toyznt

00:06:12.021 --> 00:06:14.360
un m'hot nisht gevust vu zey zenen ahingekumen.

00:06:14.434 --> 00:06:15.660
nor nakher

00:06:15.818 --> 00:06:18.186
hot men zikh meshaer geven az dos iz oykhet

00:06:18.186 --> 00:06:19.254
SOBIBOR.

00:06:19.294 --> 00:06:21.735
bay di lets- di ⟨nenste⟩ statsye fun

00:06:21.808 --> 00:06:23.877
fun Brisk iz geven SOBIBOR.

00:06:24.171 --> 00:06:26.443
vifl mentshn hot men avekgefirt

00:06:26.483 --> 00:06:27.152
fun

00:06:26.888 --> 00:06:29.750
demolts ven men hot fun ayer mishpokhe genumen?

00:06:29.959 --> 00:06:32.116
tsvishn dray un fir toyznt

00:06:32.116 --> 00:06:33.413
UNK fun Byale.

00:06:35.190 --> 00:06:39.116
s'iz gegangen kinder, s'iz geven kinder un alte, s'iz gevezn

00:06:39.122 --> 00:06:42.949
m'hot fil mentshn aroysgefirt, bakante UNK

00:06:42.949 --> 00:06:44.628
m'hot nisht gevust vu zey zenen aheymgekumen.

00:06:44.628 --> 00:06:45.632
ikh hob nokh

00:06:45.632 --> 00:06:47.885
dem letstn tog in der fri

00:06:47.885 --> 00:06:51.480
hot men, azoy vi mayn shver hot mir gezogt, mayn SCHWIEGERVATER hot mir gezogt

00:06:51.480 --> 00:06:54.810
az s'iz im kalt in di fis. er hot nisht UNK zeyer kalt

00:06:55.137 --> 00:06:56.987
hob ikh gehat a por SCHUH

00:06:57.178 --> 00:07:00.007
vos ikh hob gekrign oyfn BEZUGSCHEIN, NEUE SCHUH

00:07:01.093 --> 00:07:03.787
oyf BEZUGSCHEIN hob ikh gekrign, fun mayn arbet

00:07:04.215 --> 00:07:06.077
hob ikh avekgetrogn di SCHUH.

00:07:06.077 --> 00:07:08.051
ikh hob nokh arayngeleygt in

00:07:08.051 --> 00:07:10.067
in di SCHUH hob ikh nokh arayngeleygt

00:07:10.067 --> 00:07:14.531
kh'hob gehat a UNK leder tsu leygn SOHLEN, zog ikh vu m'vet kumen UNK zayn shusters

00:07:14.531 --> 00:07:17.135
tsi zey veln mir adortn, ⟨kenen⟩ leygn SOHLEN oyf dem

00:07:17.378 --> 00:07:19.670
UND ikh hob oykhet arayngeleygt sakharin

00:07:19.670 --> 00:07:23.965
sakharin hobn mir get- ge- gegebn im mit als ZAHLUNGS mitl

00:07:23.965 --> 00:07:26.552
⟨ets FAHRTS zikh arum⟩ kenen krign epes andersh

00:07:26.625 --> 00:07:31.237
hob ikh mitgegebn sakharin vos iz gevezn in gesheft, in gevelb bay mayn shviger

00:07:31.237 --> 00:07:34.207
hot zi mir mitgegebn. mir hobn nisht gevust. mir hobn zikh nokh nisht

00:07:34.207 --> 00:07:36.932
⟨gornisht⟩ forgeshtelt az me farnikhtet mentshn

00:07:36.932 --> 00:07:39.345
az me shikt zey ergets oyf, in a farnikhtungs lager

00:07:39.345 --> 00:07:41.148
vayl biz yetst hobn mir gezen

00:07:41.222 --> 00:07:43.683
di f- di fartribene fun

00:07:43.683 --> 00:07:44.763
Suvalk

00:07:44.763 --> 00:07:48.084
fun Serotsk

00:07:48.225 --> 00:07:51.195
UND fun Mlave di ale hot men

00:07:51.195 --> 00:07:54.385
bay undz gelozt lebn, hobn mir gemeynt zey forn oykhet oyf a enlekhn

00:07:54.385 --> 00:07:56.690
oyf a enlekhes ort ergets

00:07:57.473 --> 00:08:00.859
azoy iz dos. ALSO do yetst lomir umkern zikh tsu

00:08:01.067 --> 00:08:04.284
tsvey un fertsik, erev sukes.

00:08:05.640 --> 00:08:06.596
ikh

00:08:06.703 --> 00:08:09.138
gez- hob gezen vos se greyt zikh.

00:08:09.138 --> 00:08:13.329
oykh mayn bruder iz gekumen damolslt tsu mir. ikh ho- a yingerer bruder, Botshe

00:08:13.774 --> 00:08:16.538
hot er mir, hob ikh im geredt tsu im, hob ikh im gezogt

00:08:16.538 --> 00:08:19.178
"du bist eyn un eyntsik aleyn.

00:08:19.178 --> 00:08:21.838
ikh hob flikhtn fun a familye. ikh hob a f-

00:08:21.838 --> 00:08:23.198
froy, ikh hob a kind.

00:08:23.198 --> 00:08:25.178
kh'hob a UNK do, a SCHWIEGERMUTTER.

00:08:25.178 --> 00:08:28.820
du bist eyner aleyn. WARUM vartstu? WARUM zitsstu azoy lang

00:08:28.827 --> 00:08:29.631
do?"

00:08:29.670 --> 00:08:32.586
er iz gevezn a g-oykhet a, oysgedint a soldat.

00:08:32.586 --> 00:08:34.113
un er iz geven farletst

00:08:34.113 --> 00:08:35.708
als KRIEGSINVALID

00:08:35.708 --> 00:08:38.653
iz er gevezn tsvey SCHUSS hot er gekrign in di fis

00:08:38.653 --> 00:08:39.935
fun a FLUGZEUG

00:08:39.935 --> 00:08:41.712
ven m'hot

00:08:42.360 --> 00:08:45.492
ven er iz geven oyfn front ergets unter Mlave.

00:08:45.668 --> 00:08:49.892
hot men, iz er, ho- hot er gefirt, er iz geven alts a UNK

00:08:49.892 --> 00:08:52.018
hot er gedint in armey, hot er gefirt

00:08:52.018 --> 00:08:55.196
a vogn mit TROTIL, oyfrays materyal

00:08:55.371 --> 00:08:57.559
iz er aropgeshprungen fun vogn

00:08:57.801 --> 00:09:03.380
vayle in vogn ven UNK treft a kugl, volt, volt oyfgerisn der gantser WAGEN

00:09:03.690 --> 00:09:05.051
ferd un WAGEN

00:09:05.260 --> 00:09:06.418
UND

00:09:06.778 --> 00:09:09.635
er hot zikh ge- farshtekt oyfn feld

00:09:09.635 --> 00:09:12.796
UND dort hot er gekrign tsvey SCHUSSEN. eyn SCHUSS in di

00:09:12.837 --> 00:09:14.215
FERSE

00:09:14.355 --> 00:09:16.284
UND eyn SCHUSS in fus.

00:09:16.284 --> 00:09:17.471
di fis

00:09:17.545 --> 00:09:21.313
in di WAGEN, ⟨ven es hot dos⟩ gekrign, hot zikh bald farheylt

00:09:21.313 --> 00:09:23.777
dergegn in di FERSE, hot es

00:09:23.777 --> 00:09:26.468
tseshmetert im di knokhn

00:09:26.468 --> 00:09:28.240
un DASS hot zikh nisht farheylt

00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:29.739
di gantse tsayt

00:09:31.787 --> 00:09:36.945
ALSO az er iz gekumen tsu mir. er hot gearbet in a, als tishler, er hot gearbet in a

00:09:37.288 --> 00:09:39.057
verk f- in

00:09:39.057 --> 00:09:41.335
in a ts- zegl verk

00:09:41.335 --> 00:09:42.567
vu m'hot gemakht

00:09:42.567 --> 00:09:45.365
oyfn front hot men aroysgeshikt ⟨ZARGEN⟩

00:09:45.523 --> 00:09:48.200
UND tslomim,

00:09:48.274 --> 00:09:49.545
g- KREUTZEN

00:09:49.545 --> 00:09:54.073
vos m'hot geshtelt ergets oyfn, di frontn, vu m'hot ge- gefalene

00:09:54.417 --> 00:09:56.025
un er hot derbay gearbet

00:09:56.025 --> 00:09:59.270
iz er gekumen yetst tsu mir. s'hot z- iz gevezn f-

00:09:59.665 --> 00:10:00.874
fraytik

00:10:01.369 --> 00:10:03.320
UND er iz gekumen tsu mir

00:10:03.580 --> 00:10:09.362
UND ikh hob im gegebn a bisl sakharin UNK mit, ikh gedenk nisht vos nokh ikh hob im mitgegebn. sakharin iz gevezn a

00:10:09.553 --> 00:10:12.112
a tog teglekher, ⟨s'iz⟩ azoy gut vi broyt.

00:10:13.215 --> 00:10:15.470
ikh gedenk nisht vos nokh ikh hob im gegebn

00:10:15.628 --> 00:10:19.959
un ikh hob im geshtelt di frage "far vos zitsstu nokh do? oyf vos vartstu?"

00:10:20.134 --> 00:10:22.912
er iz gevezn, tsvey yor iz er gevezn

00:10:23.003 --> 00:10:24.383
oyfn land

00:10:24.383 --> 00:10:25.725
in POLUBICZE.

00:10:25.725 --> 00:10:30.017
er hot gearbet dortn als, bay BAUEREN

00:10:30.394 --> 00:10:32.618
landvirtshaft arbet geholfn

00:10:32.618 --> 00:10:34.213
vayl in ershtn yor f-

00:10:34.213 --> 00:10:35.622
in ershtn yor

00:10:35.622 --> 00:10:37.138
in eyn un VIERZIG

00:10:37.228 --> 00:10:39.432
hobn di DEUTSCHEN erloybt

00:10:39.507 --> 00:10:42.271
yidn tsu nemen tsu di arbet oyfn land.

00:10:42.271 --> 00:10:47.291
un s'hobn gearbet, m'hot gezen yidn vu m'iz gegangen, vu m'iz geshtanen. ven UNK mir flegn geyn

00:10:47.291 --> 00:10:50.806
oyfn land mit, mit undzere gesheftn, mit undzer

00:10:51.268 --> 00:10:52.910
handl vos mir hobn gefirt

00:10:52.910 --> 00:10:54.024
oyfn dorf

00:10:54.024 --> 00:10:56.392
flegn mir trefn oyfn veg

00:10:56.466 --> 00:10:59.919
flegn ⟨undz⟩ UNK glaykh yidishe yinglekh opshteln.

00:11:01.022 --> 00:11:06.216
"vos hert zikh, yidn? vos makht ir, yidn? ikh bin fun Varshe.

00:11:06.216 --> 00:11:10.190
ikh voyn oyf di ⟨SZMULOMILA⟩ dortn, aza un aza adres."

00:11:10.190 --> 00:11:13.470
zey hobn zikh gegebn tsi ken- zey hobn gezen in undz az mir y- zenen yidn.

00:11:15.231 --> 00:11:20.451
un azoy hot men iberal getrofn oyf di f- oyf di lender hot men getrof- oyfn land hot men getrofn.

00:11:20.451 --> 00:11:22.461
yidn hobn gearbet, mayn bruder oykhet.

00:11:22.461 --> 00:11:26.295
a tsveyter bruder a elterer hot gearbet oykhet dort oyfn dorf, oyf a tsveyt ort

00:11:30.132 --> 00:11:33.737
az ikh bin avek fun di, fun di, vegn vos hob ikh geredt?

00:11:33.430 --> 00:11:38.580
ir hot gevolt redn vegn ven es hot zikh ongehoybn di tsveyte UNK

00:11:37.692 --> 00:11:40.673
di UNK ALSO mayn bruder der

00:11:41.016 --> 00:11:46.106
er hot ge- er iz shoyn gevezn biz eyn un fertsik, biz shpet eyn un fertsik

