hobn gevoynt bay undz in undzer voynung.

00:25:29.359 --> 00:25:33.839
i- az zi iz arib- un zi hot nisht gev- zi hot nisht gekent keyn ander ort, di Perl.

00:25:33.839 --> 00:25:37.279
ven m'hot ir aroysgeshtoysn fun, fun di reye

