ikh zog tsu mayn vayb "her zikh oys vos. mir zenen farfalene mentshn. mir kenen

00:27:18.132 --> 00:27:20.857
do antdekt vern tsu yede minut fun, fun, fun

00:27:20.857 --> 00:27:21.861
zhandarmeri

00:27:21.861 --> 00:27:25.250
UND gevezn, gevust hot mir, der PIETRUCZUK hot mir dertseylt

00:27:25.425 --> 00:27:30.231
az vemen me treft a farshtektn, shist men. ⟨koym⟩ s'iz do a tate mit a kind oyf di elter

00:27:30.231 --> 00:27:31.193
mit kinder

00:27:31.193 --> 00:27:33.181
shist men tsum ershtn di kinder

00:27:33.542 --> 00:27:37.251
un kedey di eltern zoln zikh ⟨hobn⟩ dos

00:27:37.251 --> 00:27:38.868
dos agmes nefesh

00:27:38.892 --> 00:27:42.432
azoy dertseylt, dertseylt im az me hot a geviser KANTORn

00:27:42.432 --> 00:27:44.550
KANTOR mit di tokhter zikh

00:27:44.550 --> 00:27:46.760
farshtekt un m'hot zey gefunen ergets

00:27:46.760 --> 00:27:51.519
hot men tsum ershtn ir foter's kegnvart hot men di tokhter dershosn

00:27:51.519 --> 00:27:52.604
