azoy oykh, azoy az ⟨m- undz⟩ vet men mit undz ⟨zikh⟩ trefn

00:27:56.252 --> 00:27:59.054
s'iz do gute shkheynim vos zey voltn undz gevolt helfn

00:27:59.054 --> 00:28:01.970
ober s'iz do shkheynim vos zey zenen shlekhte. zey veln undz

00:28:02.230 --> 00:28:06.842
yede tsayt kenen mir ge- zog ikh UNK di eyntsike meglekhkeytn tsu blaybn lebn

00:28:06.842 --> 00:28:08.057
iz undzer kind.

00:28:08.057 --> 00:28:09.289
zi iz a meydl

00:28:09.289 --> 00:28:14.138
zi hot nisht keyn tseykhn, keyn, keyn

00:28:14.278 --> 00:28:16.027
kh'hob gemeynt keyn, keyn

00:28:16.303 --> 00:28:19.824
CIELESNA, s'heyst, keyn kerperlekhn tseykhn

00:28:19.864 --> 00:28:23.084
azoy, un redn redt es zikh mit di internatsyonale

00:28:23.084 --> 00:28:24.394
kinder SPRACHE

